Class SimulatorGUI

java.lang.Object
javafx.application.Application
view.SimulatorGUI
All Implemented Interfaces:
ISimulatorUI
public class SimulatorGUI extends javafx.application.Application implements ISimulatorUI
SimulatorGUI class is responsible for the graphical user interface of the simulator. It extends Application and implements ISimulatorUI.
